Author: TotallyNotARadar
Text: Right like one of my friends eight six of these cookies I made. They were 120 each. We had dinner right after too. She’s totally normal weighted too. It’s crazy that some people have functioning self-regulation

Author: MontmajourLaCrau
Text: Me too! I can usually gauge my friends lunches and can kind of guess they’re tdee’s. I know it’d be inappropriate to say anything but, sometimes they’ll have like 800cal lunches and I’m just floored.
